headline: Uber’s Nationwide Hibbett Deal Might Change the Case for Investing in Uber Technologies (UBER)
summary: Hibbett, Inc. announced a nationwide partnership with Uber Technologies, Inc., rolling out nearly 900 retail locations for on-demand athletic fashion, footwear, and accessories delivery via the Uber Eats platform across the US. This collaboration underlines Uber Eats' expansion beyond restaurant delivery, reflecting its ambition to become a comprehensive retail destination for lifestyle and sports products.
